import React from 'react'; import './Why.css' function Why() { return (

Why InCTFCon ?

There are a lot of untapped opportunities for people to take up the role of safeguarding a digital space.

There is a heavy global demand for cybersecurity professionals but there aren’t many skilled people out there. This job pays really well!

The projected growth of employment in cybersecurity is estimated to be around 3.5 million new job opportunities by 2022.

The danger of a cyber pandemic is imminent and the world needs cybersecurity professionals to protect the world from such an attack – just like a superhero!
